    "description": "<p>Base Camp Digital, founded in Singapore in 2018 (formerly Ploy Asia), is a leading IT Solutions and Delivery company operating across Asia, with offices in Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, and Thailand.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br>\nWe provide targeted expertise for successful project outcomes tailored to modern technological demands.</p>\n<p><br>\nOur core delivery expertise focuses on high-growth areas:<br>\nEnterprise Software Implementation: Delivery and support for major ERP/CRM systems, including deep platform expertise in:<br>\nSAP, Salesforce, Oracle, Workday, Pega, Microsoft, and ServiceNow.<br>\nBespoke Software Development: Custom application development using key technologies like Java, .NET, and open-source stacks. Inluding Software Testing Manual and Automation.<br>\nData, Analytics, and AI: Services spanning Data Engineering, Data Analysis, and advanced Artificial Intelligence (AI) solutions (Machine Learning, Computer Vision, LLMs).<br>\nInfrastructure Services: Full-range support, from basic desktop to complex Data Centre management.</p>",
